<main class="container">
  <h2 class="mt-3 text-teal">About Us</h2>
  <hr />
  <h3>Welcome to the Complaint Management System</h3>

  <p>
    The <strong>Complaint Management System</strong> is designed to streamline
    the process of lodging, tracking, and managing complaints for both users and
    administrators. Our platform ensures that every complaint is registered,
    addressed, and resolved efficiently, providing transparency and a seamless
    experience for all users.
  </p>
  <h3 class="lead">Our Purpose</h3>

  <p>
    We understand that managing complaints can often be a challenging and
    time-consuming process for both organizations and individuals. Our goal is
    to simplify this process by providing a centralized platform where users can
    easily submit their complaints, and administrators can manage and resolve
    them effectively.
  </p>

  <h3 class="lead">Key Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>User-Friendly Interface:</strong> Whether you’re an admin or a
      regular user, our platform offers a simple and intuitive interface for
      lodging and managing complaints. - **Role-Based Access**: - **Admins**
      have access to a comprehensive **Dashboard** where they can view, manage,
      and resolve complaints. - **Users** are directed to their **Complaints**
      page where they can submit new complaints and track the status of their
      existing ones.
    </li>

    <li>
      <strong> Secure Authentication: </strong> We use industry-standard
      <em>Passport.js</em> for user authentication, ensuring that your data is
      safe and your account is secure.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Real-Time Tracking:</strong> Users can track the progress of their
      complaints in real-time, from submission to resolution, ensuring
      transparency and peace of mind.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Notifications and Alerts:</strong> Stay informed about the status
      of your complaints with timely notifications and updates.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Centralized Management:</strong> For admins, managing complaints
      has never been easier.
    </li>
    <li>
      The <strong>Dashboard</strong> provides a holistic view of all complaints,
      allowing for quick action and better service delivery.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <hr />

  <h3 class="lead">Why Choose Us?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Efficiency</strong>: By automating many aspects of complaint
      management, our system saves time and reduces administrative overhead.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Transparency:</strong> Our goal is to foster trust between users
      and organizations by providing full visibility into the status and
      resolution of complaints.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Scalability:</strong> Built on Node.js, Express, and MongoDB, our
      platform is highly scalable, making it suitable for both small businesses
      and larger organizations.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Customizable:</strong> We know that every organization has unique
      needs. Our system is designed to be easily customizable, allowing you to
      adapt it to your specific requirements.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="lead">Our Vision</h3>
  <p>
    At the heart of our platform is a commitment to making the process of
    raising and resolving complaints as smooth and efficient as possible. We
    believe that every user’s concern matters, and we strive to provide a system
    that empowers users and enhances service delivery.
  </p>

